rows.label: qst400304_msg0001
rows.name:
Please defeat the Juppen Krabble
on Lasqam Island for me.

rows.label: qst400304_msg0002
rows.name:
You can see Lasqam Island to the
left as you exit the city entrance.

rows.label: qst400304_msg0003
rows.name:
You can go around the plains, but there's
also a shortcut across the branches,
though the footing is a bit narrow.

rows.label: qst400304_msg0102
rows.name:
It seems you safely defeated
the Juppen Krabble. My judgment
wasn't wrong after all.

rows.label: qst400304_msg0103
rows.name:
Here is the Perfect Range
Sensor, as promised.

rows.label: qst400304_msg0104
rows.name:
It's from my grandpa's time, so
it's a bit dusty, but it should
work without any problems.

rows.label: qst400304_msg0105
rows.name: Thank you. You've been a great help.
